First you must install Turbogears and everything it depends on, luckily this
is extremely simple.  For those on "nix" system simply run the ez_setup.py
script as follows

sudo easy_install.py -f http://www.turbogears.org/download/index.html --script-dir /usr/local/bin TurboGears

Congratulations.

For those that are still having some trouble or do not use Linux goto

http://www.turbogears.org.nyud.net:8090/download/index.html

for more information.
